    "item": [
        {
            "name": "1. AUTH",
            "description": "Authentication endpoints for user registration and login",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Register User",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"developer\",\n  \"email\": \"developer@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123!\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Developer User\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "auth",
                                "register"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Register a new user in the system\n\n**Request Body:**\n- username: unique username\n- email: valid email address\n- password: strong password\n- fullName: user's full name\n\n**Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"user-uuid\",\n  \"username\": \"developer\",\n  \"email\": \"developer@example.com\",\n  \"message\": \"User registered successfully\"\n}\n```"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Login User",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    pm.environment.set(\"token\", jsonData.token);",
                                    "    console.log(\"✓ JWT Token extracted and saved\");",
                                    "    console.log(\"Token: \" + jsonData.token.substring(0, 20) + \"...\");",
                                    "} else {",
                                    "    console.log(\"✗ Login failed: \" + pm.response.code);",
                                    "}"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "auth",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Authenticate user and obtain JWT token\n\n**Request Body:**\n- username: admin / developer\n- password: user's password\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"expiresIn\": 3600\n}\n```\n\n**IMPORTANT:** This request automatically extracts the JWT token and saves it to the `token` environment variable for use in subsequent requests."
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
