                                "devices"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Create a new IoT device\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Request Body:**\n- name: device name\n- type: temperature | humidity | vibration | multi-sensor\n- location: physical location\n- description: device description\n- serialNumber: unique serial number\n- status: ACTIVE | INACTIVE\n\n**Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"device-uuid\",\n  \"name\": \"Sensor A\",\n  \"type\": \"temperature\",\n  \"location\": \"Madrid\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-31T10:00:00Z\"\n}\n```"
                    }
                },
