                        "description": "Get paginated list of all devices\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- page: page number (0-indexed)\n- size: items per page\n- sort: sort criteria (createdAt,desc | name,asc)\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"content\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n      \"name\": \"Sensor A\",\n      \"type\": \"temperature\",\n      \"location\": \"Madrid\",\n      \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n      \"lastDataPoint\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"totalElements\": 15,\n  \"totalPages\": 1,\n  \"currentPage\": 0\n}\n```"
                    }
