                        "description": "Get detailed information about a specific device\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Path Parameter:**\n- id: device UUID\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n  \"name\": \"Sensor A\",\n  \"type\": \"temperature\",\n  \"location\": \"Madrid\",\n  \"serialNumber\": \"SNS-2026-001\",\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"description\": \"Temperature sensor in main warehouse\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-15T08:00:00Z\",\n  \"lastActivity\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"dataPointsCount\": 15432\n}\n```"
                    }
