        {
            "name": "3. TELEMETRY",
            "description": "Device telemetry data ingestion",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Send Telemetry Data",
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "bearer",
                            "bearer": [
                                {
                                    "key": "token",
                                    "value": "{{token}}",
                                    "type": "string"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:45Z\",\n  \"temperature\": 25.5,\n  \"humidity\": 60,\n  \"vibration\": 0.02,\n  \"pressure\": 1013.25,\n  \"luminosity\": 450\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/telemetry",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "telemetry"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Ingest telemetry data from a device\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Request Body:**\n- deviceId: UUID of the IoT device\n- timestamp: ISO 8601 timestamp\n- temperature: temperature in Celsius (optional)\n- humidity: humidity percentage (optional)\n- vibration: vibration level in mm/s (optional)\n- pressure: atmospheric pressure in hPa (optional)\n- luminosity: light level in lux (optional)\n\n**Response (202):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"telemetry-uuid\",\n  \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:45Z\",\n  \"status\": \"RECEIVED\"\n}\n```\n\n**Note:** Data is asynchronously processed by Kafka and anomaly detection pipeline."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Batch Telemetry Data",
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "bearer",
                            "bearer": [
                                {
                                    "key": "token",
                                    "value": "{{token}}",
                                    "type": "string"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            },
                            {
                                "key": "Authorization",
                                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "[\n  {\n    \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:45Z\",\n    \"temperature\": 25.5,\n    \"humidity\": 60\n  },\n  {\n    \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-2\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:45Z\",\n    \"temperature\": 28.3,\n    \"humidity\": 55\n  },\n  {\n    \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-3\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-31T10:30:45Z\",\n    \"temperature\": 22.1,\n    \"humidity\": 65\n  }\n]"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/telemetry/batch",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "v1",
                                "telemetry",
                                "batch"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Ingest multiple telemetry records in a single request\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Request Body:** Array of telemetry objects\n\n**Response (202):**\n```json\n{\n  \"totalReceived\": 3,\n  \"successful\": 3,\n  \"failed\": 0\n}\n```"
                    }
                }
            ]
