                        "description": "Retrieve all alerts in the system\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- status: ACTIVE | RESOLVED | ACKNOWLEDGED\n- page: page number\n- size: items per page\n- severity: CRITICAL | HIGH | MEDIUM | LOW\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"content\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"alert-uuid-1\",\n      \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n      \"type\": \"ANOMALY_DETECTED\",\n      \"severity\": \"HIGH\",\n      \"message\": \"Temperature anomaly detected: 45.2°C (normal: 20-30°C)\",\n      \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-31T10:45:00Z\",\n      \"acknowledgedAt\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"totalElements\": 5,\n  \"totalPages\": 1\n}\n```"
                    }
                },
