                                {
                                    "key": "start",
                                    "value": "2026-03-24T00:00:00Z"
                                },
                                {
                                    "key": "end",
                                    "value": "2026-03-31T23:59:59Z"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get time series data for charting and analysis\n\n**Authorization:** Bearer Token required\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- metric: temperature | humidity | vibration | pressure\n- interval: 5m | 15m | 1h | 6h | 24h\n- start: ISO 8601 start timestamp\n- end: ISO 8601 end timestamp\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"deviceId\": \"device-uuid-1\",\n  \"metric\": \"temperature\",\n  \"interval\": \"1h\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\"timestamp\": \"2026-03-24T00:00:00Z\", \"value\": 23.5},\n    {\"timestamp\": \"2026-03-24T01:00:00Z\", \"value\": 22.8},\n    {\"timestamp\": \"2026-03-24T02:00:00Z\", \"value\": 21.9}\n  ]\n}\n```"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "6. ML API",
            "description": "Machine Learning API for anomaly detection and predictions",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Get Model Info",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{ml_url}}/model-info",
                            "host": [
                                "{{ml_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "model-info"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Get information about the ML model\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"model_name\": \"Isolation Forest Anomaly Detector\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"accuracy\": 0.9847,\n  \"features\": [\"temperature\", \"humidity\", \"vibration\", \"pressure\"],\n  \"threshold\": 0.75,\n  \"trained_on\": \"2026-03-15\",\n  \"samples_trained\": 250000\n}\n```"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Predict Anomaly",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"temperature\": 45.2,\n  \"humidity\": 75,\n  \"vibration\": 0.85,\n  \"pressure\": 1010.5\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{ml_url}}/predict",
                            "host": [
                                "{{ml_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "predict"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Predict if the given sensor values indicate an anomaly\n\n**Request Body:**\n- temperature: temperature in Celsius\n- humidity: relative humidity percentage\n- vibration: vibration level in mm/s\n- pressure: atmospheric pressure in hPa\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"is_anomaly\": true,\n  \"anomaly_score\": 0.92,\n  \"confidence\": 0.95,\n  \"reasoning\": \"Temperature is 15.2°C above normal operating range\",\n  \"recommendations\": [\n    \"Check sensor calibration\",\n    \"Verify environmental conditions\",\n    \"Review historical data\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Status Codes:**\n- 200: Prediction successful\n- 400: Invalid input data\n- 500: Model inference error"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Train Model",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"training_data_path\": \"/data/processed/training_set.parquet\",\n  \"validation_split\": 0.2,\n  \"random_state\": 42\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{ml_url}}/train",
                            "host": [
                                "{{ml_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "train"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Trigger ML model retraining\n\n**Request Body:**\n- training_data_path: path to training data\n- validation_split: validation data percentage\n- random_state: random seed for reproducibility\n\n**Response (202):**\n```json\n{\n  \"job_id\": \"training-job-uuid\",\n  \"status\": \"TRAINING_IN_PROGRESS\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-03-31T11:00:00Z\",\n  \"estimated_duration_minutes\": 30\n}\n```"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Get Training Status",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{ml_url}}/training/training-job-uuid",
                            "host": [
                                "{{ml_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "training",
                                "training-job-uuid"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Check the status of a training job\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"job_id\": \"training-job-uuid\",\n  \"status\": \"COMPLETED\",\n  \"accuracy\": 0.9847,\n  \"precision\": 0.9812,\n  \"recall\": 0.9892,\n  \"f1_score\": 0.9852,\n  \"completed_at\": \"2026-03-31T11:28:00Z\"\n}\n```"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
